          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Abandoned Well Remediation Research and Development Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to establish a research, development, and demonstration program with respect to (1) data collection on the location of abandoned oil or gas wells; (2) the plugging, remediation, reclamation, and repurposing of the wells; and (3) mitigating potential environmental impacts of documented and undocumented abandoned wells.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
